    "major_stream_name": "Arts",
    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "The first thing I liked the most about the college is the functioning of the societies especially the Placement Cell. They will give you the experience of the corporate world at the cell. Being a part of it is a very developing experience.",
          "name": "Aditi Upadhyay",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "Being a women's college IPCW places a strong emphasis for empowering women , both academically and personally through various seminars and workshops.",
          "name": "Rasha Rasha",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "I like the extracurricular activities about my college it offers a wide range of opportunities like the debate club , cultural societies and sport activities",
          "name": "Rasha Rasha",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "The campus is know for its greenery and architecture i like that about my college.it also has well maintained classrooms , libraries ,laboratories and other modern facilities",
          "name": "Rasha Rasha",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "The college is good for those who are really studious . The faculty of college is also really good . I'm pursuing Bcom hons and the commerce faculty is really very helpful and friendly.",
          "name": "Jahnvi Maheshwari",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "The security of a women's college; giving women a freedom to make their own opinions, dress as they wanted and learn without troubles.",
          "name": "Jahnvi Sehgal",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "Facilities- One of the best things is that this college has all Facilities like sports complex, library, canteen, gym, conference hall, auditorium etc",
          "name": "Janvi Devgun",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "Societies- the college has many societies that cover everybody's area of interest.",
          "name": "Janvi Devgun",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "Faculty- The faculty of every department is well educated, almost every single teacher has done Phd. They are helpful as well",
          "name": "Janvi Devgun",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "College campus- it is the most beautiful campus for sure.",
          "name": "Janvi Devgun",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "In timetable there are gaps for example you have class from 1-2 then its from 4-5 sonit gets really annoying",
          "name": "Review Ninja",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "Don't like the restriction and rules that bound ya to many extent",
          "name": "Priya Jaiswal",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "And i disliked the faculties. The way some of them behave and their poor knowledge of certain topics.i also disliked the way the pronounce certain words it made me doubt if im studying in a central university",
          "name": "Rasha Rasha",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "And i disliked the academic environment of Indraprastha college its highly competitive that makes the students stressful who prefer a relaxed and calm environment",
          "name": "Rasha Rasha",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "I disliked the strict rules and regulations regarding attendance, discipline,and hostel regulations which might feel restrictive to some students",
          "name": "Rasha Rasha",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "Some of classrooms are not ventilated plus the beaches are also not comfortable.",
          "name": "Jahnvi Maheshwari",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "I'm living in hostel and to be honest the hostel is expensive which needs to be lower in price",
          "name": "Jahnvi Maheshwari",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "I somewhere don't like the management of the college . Sometimes even the official things took so much time which really irritates the students as well as faculty.",
          "name": "Jahnvi Maheshwari",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "The fests and college functions were not open for other colleges. They were not as good as other University colleges.",
          "name": "Jahnvi Sehgal",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "Delays-The only thing that i disliked was that for some works like for example if you have to submit noc for your internship, they take a lot of time to submit it and give the noc.",
          "name": "Janvi Devgun",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        }
      ]
    },
    "affiliated_to": {
      "name": "Delhi University, New Delhi"
    }
  },
